projects.name: Blood Bank Management
projects.description: Designed and developed a comprehensive Blood Bank Management System. Utilized front-end technologies for an intuitive user interface, back-end expertise for robust data management, and JavaScript for dynamic functionality. Implemented features to streamline blood donation processes, inventory management, and donor tracking, enhancing operational efficiency.

projects.name: Spam Detection
projects.description: Directed a project targeting spam detection utilizing K-Nearest Neighbors (KNN) and Random Forest machine learning models. Implemented KNN to classify emails by their similarity to labeled datasets, achieving notable accuracy in distinguishing spam messages. Deployed Random Forest for its ensemble learning approach, effectively discerning spam through the aggregation of multiple decision trees.

experiences.description: Conducted impactful research on Resonant Tunneling Diode using Silvaco and Next Nano software, showcasing expertise in semiconductor device simulation. Utilized resonant tunneling diodes to enable terahertz imaging, showcasing proficiency in high-frequency applications for advanced image generation. Applied hands-on experience in electronic design automation tools, enhancing proficiency in semiconductor device modeling.
